{"tid":865523,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2010年後啲細路係咪老豆老母唔識教","createTime":"2018-10-17T06:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T07:12:39.000Z","uid":115323,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"42cfdf99dffa7afb2d1739bd79a3c641006d32c9","tid":865523,"uid":115323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T06:45:15.000Z","msg":"啱啱經過便利店門口 見到一班細路仔入去搗亂 <br />\n拎住個足球又拍又踢<br />\n其中一個便利店職員就話 唔做你地生意快啲走<br />\n班小朋友就行到門口聲稱要拎走啲出面啲零食<br />\n另一個職員就話 再搞就報警<br />\n個細佬竟然話 打去報警浪費警力呀 番去訓教啦死阿姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家啲小朋友係咪冇人管教？ 唔識教就咪撚生啦<br />\n基本禮貌修養 完全冇 番大陸呢啲細佬見得多 而家香港愈黎愈多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9533e539c30aa7c68df7e67483b3246536498a","tid":865523,"uid":164163,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T06:46:55.000Z","msg":"0分重作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d563233fcfeaff6dedfda6b3f3cd305b7b7dd70a","tid":865523,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T06:48:01.000Z","msg":"D童黨不嬲都有架啦"},{"pid":"a5519975fe4e1b00b034eadfebcd9e810b916718","tid":865523,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:01:02.000Z","msg":"咩年代都有呢啲人啦 又關幾多後咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3ad1a83e9961e018d21e673f0f07f1c3ba904f","tid":865523,"uid":104171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:05:34.000Z","msg":"但而家啲細路係大膽左"},{"pid":"9b99012b0f5e2f160e855f01648824748e2d9cc5","tid":865523,"uid":115323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a5519975fe4e1b00b034eadfebcd9e810b916718","tid":865523,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:01:02.000Z","msg":"咩年代都有呢啲人啦 又關幾多後咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:12:39.000Z","msg":"吓 以前真係唔見有咁多喎 <br />\n成班都係支那仔"